.cn/mmbiz_png/y5gDUibOr9AVhXfO5f4vxtAgXPzaYOcUibWbN13DnsxA9Hw05ZpWEAINv8Kv5aHGBSkIpA38WQ4YZiayqTPy7aRBA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p></section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这是Facebook的华人高管Julie Zhuo曾经画过的两幅图。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">从上面两张图片里，我们可以感受到两种截然不同的工作状态。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">前者呈现的是一种杂乱无章，摸不着头脑的状态，后者则相对有条理。</span></p></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">如果把这两张图所展示的工作状态对应到保险销售的工作上来看，前者更像是初期新人的工作模式，后者则偏向MDRT精英的工作模式。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">新人在工作中，从最初的打电话到最后签单，过程往往会显得错综复杂，没有一个明确的方向和头绪。很多时候可能绕了一圈之后发现又回到原点，做了很多无用功。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">而作为一名MDRT精英，更多的是目标导向。在一个大的目标前提下，层层拆解，环环相扣，最终达成目标。避开了不少弯路，往往会使得工作效率和效果都提高不少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\">造成这种差异的关键因素在于背后的专业训练。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">咱们许多伙伴因为缺乏对专业化销售流程的了解和认知，在我们的学习和展业过程中，都有许多欠缺，因为没有经过这种专业的训练，对我们自己销售问题的诊断具有许多障碍，造成了我们的许多不便，所以我们和客户交流的时候都没有共同语言。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">现在，对于如何开拓客户、接触客户、促成签单等会感到困惑的伙伴们有解啦！</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">这里有一门<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\">《专业化销售流程》</span></strong>，专门为你们而准备！</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\">这门课程有哪些特色？</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">1、通俗易懂，王辰老师将很多专业理念融合到生活中，便于大家更容易理解学习；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">2、经验丰富，19年的从业经验、数千场的线下授课，针对于代理人在新人阶段遇到的困惑，经验十分丰富；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">3、干货十足，经过课程组一个月的反复打磨，在这6小时课程里，客户开拓、接触客户、促成等等环节详细讲解，结合实例，干货满满，含金量十足；</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">4、系统学习，区别于其他老师针对于某一个板块进行简单讲解，王辰老师对整个销售流程进行了系统化的讲授。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -53px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; width: 32px; height: 32px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99); text-align: center; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background-image: url(\">1</p><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;\">这门课程适合谁？</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">适合：0基础，没有保险从业经验，或是整体从业经验匮乏<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">（少于1年）；</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;一直没有找到适合自己的开单模式的伙伴。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">不适合：从业2年以上，已经具备或养成自己的开单模式。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -53px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; width: 32px; height: 32px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99); text-align: center; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background-image: url(\">2</p><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;\">课程导师是谁？</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">王辰，著名保险教育家、寿险业资深讲师、1997年毕业于清华大学，1998年从事保险业，19年来在全国进行了数千场讲座，影响数十万保险人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -53px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; width: 32px; height: 32px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99); text-align: center; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background-image: url(\">3</p><section><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 14px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(48, 166, 99);\"><strong class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit;\">本次课程可以解决什么问题？</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">《专业化销售流程》里会讲到销售技巧，但是更多的是培养大家专业化销售流程模式的养成。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">我认为只要认真学习了这门课程，里面的内容，能够解决你新人阶段50%以上的销售方面的各种疑难杂症。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">比如：“没有客户怎么办？”“客户不见我怎么办？”“客户就是不签单怎么办？”......等等。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','',0,10.0,0,4,68,1517559885,1518366689,0,13,0,1,'/public/image/poster.jpg',0,'','/public/image/course_wxcode_72.png',1326,'rgb(38,43,45)'),(73,0,'明星保险的销售秘籍','/public/uploads/image/course/20180208/49a5bc795a4755c3249db7bc50de1fe7.jpg','','于文军老师是 文章、马伊琍等多位明星的保险顾问，21年的从业经历积累了非常多的保险销售的技巧。','/public/uploads/image/course/20180208/c316fd1f64a5fa90cd9f3540f9989cc3.png',39.90,0,'<section><section><section><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 192, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么明星们都爱买保险？</span></strong></span><br/></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多人一听到保险推销，就视为洪水猛兽，但明星们却恰恰相反。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不管是国内明星、港澳台明星还是好莱坞明星，都非常认可保险并且非常热衷于购买保险，于是有了一句经典的话<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">郎朗的双手刘翔的腿，范冰冰的脸蛋容祖儿的嘴</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">”</strong>，而且明星们保险的保额还一个比一个高。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如今，判断明星身价的方式又多了一种——看他们为自己的身体投了多少金额的保险。有的明星的保险不到位，就不进剧组开始拍摄的情况也时有发生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当年《速度与激情》的保罗，在2013年11月30日的一场车祸中不幸身亡，所幸的是保罗生前购买了大额保险，最终保罗家人获得3.1亿元的巨额保险理赔。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此前参加《奔跑吧兄弟》节目录制时，制作单位考虑到安全问题，曾为范冰冰投保了价值<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1亿元</strong>的巨额保险；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">由于明星属于高危职业，一般没有社会保险，又非常注重私密性，所以他们通常会选择高端医疗保险和高额意外伤害保险；前者可以保证明星在全球各地享受安全、私密的医疗服务，后者则可以在因演出受伤时得到理赔；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">精致的脸蛋、性感的身材等身体的每个部分，都是明星的“生财工具”甚至“身家性命”，如果稍有损伤，很可能会影响自己的前途。于是乎明星们都很热衷于为自己投保，而且会不惜重金。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">既然明星们这么热衷于购买保险，那明星的保险顾问又是何方高人呢？相比与其他保险顾问又有什么过人之处呢？明星的保险销售技巧是否可以复制于服务广大的普通客户呢？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">文章、马伊琍等各大明星、以及《老炮儿》剧组的保险顾问、平安人寿四星级讲师&nbsp;于文军老师&nbsp;将在脚印直播为大家带来一节 可复制的 明星保险顾问的销售秘籍。</span></p><p><br/></p>','',0,10.0,0,4,69,1518076564,1518177429,0,16,0,1,'/public/image/poster.jpg',0,'',NULL,268,'rgb(0,0,100)'),(74,0,'索取转介绍的正确方法和理念','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/a89b1e8418ee48c02a87d0881d49cb4f.jpeg','','很多新人业绩不稳定，是因为没有稳定的客源。开拓新客户是非常累的，如何才能轻松拥有源源不断的客源呢？据统计，MDRT成员90%的客户来自于转介绍。但是很多同学在索要转介绍名单时，要么就是拼运气，要么就硬着头皮反复追问别人，最后效果都不理想。其实转介绍是否成功取决与我们在服务客户的每一个环节中。颜丙翔老师在客户服务方面有着14年的经验，服务超过3000多个家庭。本课程的目的就是教会大家如何找到和分析转介绍过程中的问题，并针对性的去解决，从而在一个客户身上服务出源源不断的客源。','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/9739e31a0cf0ae7cdcb0076bfe067359.jpg',99.00,0,'<p>很多新人业绩不稳定，是因为没有稳定的客源。开拓新客户是非常累的，如何才能轻松拥有源源不断的客源呢？据统计，MDRT成员90%的客户来自于转介绍。但是很多同学在索要转介绍名单时，要么就是拼运气，要么就硬着头皮反复追问别人，最后效果都不理想。其实转介绍是否成功取决与我们在服务客户的每一个环节中。颜丙翔老师在客户服务方面有着14年的经验，服务超过3000多个家庭。本课程的目的就是教会大家如何找到和分析转介绍过程中的问题，并针对性的去解决，从而在一个客户身上服务出源源不断的客源。</p>','',0,10.0,0,4,70,1518155669,1518366711,0,16,0,1,'/public/image/poster.jpg',0,'','/public/image/course_wxcode_74.png',1237,'rgb(42,45,47)'),(75,0,'组织发展五大坑','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/f5d38ffd17c80f030e3d2609df171dd1.jpeg','','增员是一个长期，且是一个团队发展必不可少的步骤，不仅是收入增加的一个好方法，也是对自己人格的提升、资源的整合都是一个不错的选择！增员增起来吧，泱泱大国，14亿人等着你！先学好套路吧！','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/6447ce1a9fd9fc5ddc084741b3b08635.jpg',39.90,0,'<section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span st