b(160, 160, 160); letter-spacing: 0px;\">WEIYANBIN</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">2012年3月 &nbsp; 加盟太平人寿</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">2013年7月晋升高级经理一级</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">2017年1月晋升区域总监</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">清华大学理财规划师</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">中国人民大学经济学在读硕士</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">北京大学国学班学员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">国际认证财务顾问师</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;\">从7人的团队到200多人的团队；16个月晋升高级经理一级；魏老师到底怎么做到的?</span></strong></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">“早发现，早治疗”魏老师语重心长的说！填好一些坑，我们增员的速度才会“蹭蹭蹭”的往上升。增员的时候我们会遇到很多问题，比如增员渠道、增员方法问题，这些问题在他们团队早已经不是问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">他说就是早早的发现了这些问题，并总结了一套方法论，才能有今天的成绩。而且他们利用一些方式，让本科大学生自己找上门来加入他们团队，完全将主动权掌握到了自己的手中，最后从几百个大学生中选出最适合的20个人，留在团队继续培养。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">其实有些问题，很容易解决，他的很多方法也适用于很多别的团队，本着无私的态度，他很愿意来跟大家做这次的分享，将这些方法传授给大家，让大家赶在招聘季招到一波高质量“人才”。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">增了再增怎么玩儿</strong></span></span></p></section><section><section></section><section></section><section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">怎么利用增到的人再增，源源不断的有资源有渠道？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">魏老师所辖有41个营业组，10人以上组4个，5人以上组26个，培养出了5个高级经理，现在团队200余人，而且还在不断增加。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">在我们的聊天过程中，魏老师不断强调:“这不是我一个人的功劳！靠我一个人的资源，是绝对不能做到今天这样的！”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">是的！是团队！魏老师的团队，绝对没有锁定是单一的某个年龄段的人，团队的人员范围很广，怎么能将他们所有人的资源整合到一块，他有自己独特的一套方法！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">而且因为范围广，所以跟许多团队会有很强的共性，利用魏老师的方结合自己的团队情况，做一次资源整合的规划，还增不到员？我觉得不太可能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">增员是一个长期，且是一个团队发展必不可少的步骤，不仅是收入增加的一个好方法，也是对自己人格的提升、资源的整合都是一个不错的选择！增员增起来吧，泱泱大国，14亿人等着你！先学好套路吧！</span></p><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">适合观看对象：</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">1、保险从业人员</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">2、想要增员的业务员</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">3、想要提升自己组织发展能力的人</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></p></section></section></section></section>','',0,10.0,0,4,71,1518159260,1518248084,0,17,0,1,'/public/image/poster.jpg',0,'',NULL,1243,'rgb(193,202,201)'),(76,0,'人人都能学会的保险理财课','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/3aad86479da77f7fa9517935dfaff1b8.png','','课程名称：《人人都能学会的保险理财课》\n主讲人：陈铜\n适合观看对象：\n1、保险从业人员\n2、想要树正确的保险理财价值观的同学\n3、想要快速了解保险理财与其他理财产品不同的同学','/public/uploads/image/course/20180209/f7b4a1b567810a5ff1185de8717a1777.jpg',39.90,0,'<section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">你的客户有没有对你说过：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-size: medium; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><section><section><section><section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">—“我刚买完房子，没有多余的钱来买保险。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">—“我看别的理财公司给我推荐过一款产品，比保险的收益大得多啊！”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">—“还要等这么久才能拿到钱啊！那我还不如买基金呢！”</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">如果我们无法让客户认可保险是更适合的理财渠道，我们很有可能会失去这个客户；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">如果我们无法清晰的表达出保险与房产、银行、证券的区别与利弊，会让客户一头雾水，毫无兴趣的再继续了解下去，就只能眼睁睁的看着客户从我们手中流失。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit;\">有的业务员小伙伴就说啦：“保险可以避债避税啊，这是其他理财产品都比不了的！”</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">对，没错，保险产品是拥有它独特的形式与所谓的“债”和“税”之间的关联，但不是我们想象中的那么肤浅和简单，片面的说“保险可以避债避税”，这个观念是有误的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">当事情真正发生的时候，客户会觉得自己被骗了，从而导致客户对保险行业产生误解。长此以往，我们会逐渐的失去客户的信任与口碑。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">本着对客户认真负责的态度，怀着想留住客户的决心，我们或许也曾想过去寻找到答案，希望去更多的了解银行、证劵、房产......这些理财工具或者理财产品优缺点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">但是理财产品琳琅满目，金融术语复杂艰深，我们该如何下手？自学几乎不可能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">而且每天还要拜访客户、熟悉新的产品，已经够忙了，哪里还会有多余的时间，多余的精力再去研究保险与其他理财产品的区别！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">没有关系！</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(57, 57, 57); line-height: 28px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">请他来教你</strong></span></p></section><section><section></section><section></section><section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">脚印给你请来了这方面的明星讲师</strong></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(12, 137, 24); font-size: 18px;\">陈 铜</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">|<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">平安人寿 金牌产品专家</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">C &nbsp;H &nbsp;E &nbsp;N &nbsp;T &nbsp;O &nbsp;N &nbsp;G</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">平安保险金信托方案设计者</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">平安高峰会财富传承授课嘉宾</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">中国人民大学EMBA外请讲师</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(165, 165, 165);\">央广经济之声FM96.6特邀理财嘉宾</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">陈铜老师在理财产品与保险产品的对比上，有着很深的研究，对于保险理财的方式方法也有着自己独到的见解。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">他将这些经验与方法浓缩成了一节课，而你，只需要花一节课的时间，学会陈铜老师的见解，再次面对客户时，就能有一个完美的答案了。</span></p><p style=\"