n><section><p style=\"margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; border-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); line-height: 0em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/y5gDUibOr9AX2XA8u4WDQeHOiaRSpjLbhDxKJpQEJxNVjR3yGGuz9wwBBauwaicue2ibicLicUSbforpF6V0VRBxucDw/0?wx_fmt=png\" class=\"\"/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; padding: 0px; clear: both; border-color: rgb(198, 198, 199); line-height: 0em;\"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">前段时间无意的下载了一个App，看着手机屏幕上的秒钟一点一点轻微的移动着它的角度，下面的数字微小的增加，时间就这么具体化的展示在我的眼前。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">可能现在我们还不想用“衰老”这个词来描述时间的带给我们身体上的变化，但我们终将变老，这是一个必定的人生的课题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">你现在可逃避，但是当你回到家中，你无法避免的是时间正在以加速度的方式吸食父母的皮肤上的水分，褪去父母头发上的黑色素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">有一天突然就发现爸妈真的老了，有一天我们也会变老。</span></strong></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">因为时间就是这么公平，并不会对谁更加宽容，变老是我们必然的生命过程。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">我们无法改变我们会变老这个事实，但是我们可以选择我们如何老去。</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">也正是因为我们都逃不过这个事实，我们为什么不感同身受的去跟客户交流养老问题，预防老年问题呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">又或许，我们自己都没有意识到养老的重要性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><img src=\"/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180209/1518164877480452.png\" class=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">养老——是一个因为代理人观念不升级而导致的客户不重视的，但是又极为重要的问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180209/1518164877585306.png\" class=\"\"/></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们需要自己正视这个问题，才能更好的帮客户去规划好他们的老年生活。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><section><section><section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 17px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">重塑客户老年后的目标</strong></span></h2></section><section><img src=\"/public/uploads/ueditor/image/20180209/1518164876454142.png\" class=\"\"/></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">人的一生基本分为三个阶段：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">前20年我们基本在学校度过，为着自己能考上重点中学，名牌大学而努力奋斗；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">后40年我们在职场度过，为着我们的理想，美好的生活而坚持不懈。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">那60岁之后呢？我似乎没有仔细想过这个问题。</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p></section><section></section><section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我是靠儿女？还是靠存款？儿女压力不会大吗？存款在这个货币贬值快速的时代，够吗？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">细思极恐</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">。</span></p><section><section><section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">重疾和意外</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">是偶然风险，概率事件，但这类风险一旦发生，客户家庭必然遭受生命不可承受之重，所以重疾和意外保险是刚需。</span></p></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit;\"></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">养老是必然风险</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">，不以意志为转移的客观必然的生命过程，但是我们的客户却没有准备甚至没打算准备!</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: inherit;\"></span></p></section></section><section><section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">对于客户的老年生活我们代理人任重而道远。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们应该帮助客户重塑老年后的目标，帮助他们<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">“开启人生第三幕，活成自己想要的样子。”</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们需要帮他们想象、规划，并且告诉他们如何去实现精彩的第三幕。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们不能眼睁睁的看着客户花几十万去买保健品，备受电信诈骗，或者购买一些所谓会增值的收藏品，而将自己老年生活的规划抛诸脑后。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">但毕竟对于我们80后、90后来说，老年生活对于我们来说还是过于遥远。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">怎么和客户达成养老共识？怎么契合客户的需求？面对客户的异议我们怎么处理？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我们并没有丰富的经验去解决这些问题，所以养老金这一块我们很少触及</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><section><section><section><section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">&nbsp;周芳 太平人寿区域总经理&nbsp;</span></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\">从业年资：10年</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\">美国百万圆桌MDRT会员</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\">清华大学理财规划师（THFP）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\">太平人寿钻石级代理人</p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">周芳老师今年截止到现在，单在养老金方面的业绩已达175万，她在养老金方面有一套自己的销售流程，准备在直播当中与大家分享。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">周老师团队现在有<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">1363人</strong>，团队成员复制老师的销售流程，做的也相当不错，团队全年承保<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">9246.07万元</strong>。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></section><section></section></section><section><p class=\"135brush\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: none;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">站在未来30年后看现在，我们该如何帮客户规划老年生活？<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.2em;\">我们听听看，周老师怎么说。</span></span></p></section></section><section></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: center;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">适合观看对象：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">1、保险从业人员</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">2、想要销售养老金的伙伴</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p>','',0,10.0,0,4,74,1518165070,1518248144,0,16,0,1,'/public/image/poster.jpg',0,'',NULL,1258,'rgb(210,207,208)'),(91,0,'营销理念定乾坤','/public/uploads/image/course/20180210/3b4c5923fb36d51b816eb62da2131917.jpg','','维对于一个人的人生有着不可磨灭的作用。思维方式的不同，决定着你到底是普通保险业务员还是保险企业家；决定了你到底是月入3000与月入30万。','/public/uploads/image/course/20180210/63526ebc89c62a96a12e905ceb12bf95.jpg',39.90,0,'<section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(115, 115, 115); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 18px;\">引言<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></em></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(115, 115, 115); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px; font-size: 13px;\">思维对于一个人的人生有着不可磨灭的作用。思维方式的不同，决定着你到底是普通保险业务员还是保险企业家；决定了你到底是月入3000与月入30万。</span></p><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px;\">保险企业家到底是如何看待保险营销的？他们是如何思考的？他们成功的决定性要素是什么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px;\">「脚印」邀请了<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">信诚人寿行政总监 唐洁老师</strong>，做客脚印直播，为你拆解保险企业家的营销思维，供你学习借鉴。</span></p></section></section></section><p></p><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">思维决定命运</span></strong></span></p></section></section><section><section></section></section></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">一个月收入3千的保险业务员逆袭到月收入30万的保险企业家，到底有多难？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">前段时间我就听到这样一个小故事，我发现了其中的奥妙：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">惠勒受公司之聘担任推销顾问，他发现了一件十分有趣的事：有一位推销员，不管被公司派到什么地方去，也不管给他多少佣金，他平均所得总是每年挣五千美元，不多也不少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">因为这个推销员在一个比较小的推销区干得不错，公司就派他到一个更大的、更好的地区。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">可是第二年他与在原先那个推销区干的时候完全一样，只挣了五千美元，不多也不少。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">第三年，公司调配他到了一个最不理想的地方，但他照样还是挣了五千美元。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">惠勒通过跟这个推销员谈话，发现问题的症结不在于推销的区域，而在于他的自我评价。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">他从内心认为自己是个“每年赚五千美元”的人，当他被派到不理想的区域时，他会为五千美元而努力工作；当他被派到条件好的地区时，只要五千美元到手，他就有各种借口停步不前了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">操纵推销员的，不是作为推销员的内在实力，而是自我评价，产生的固化思维，当他有意识地转变了自己的心态，他很快地刷新了过去的记录。</span></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">从上面的这个故事，我们可以知道，我们生活的环境，接触到的人事，修砌了我们的人生观，价值观，与我们的固有思维，而我们的思维又决定了我们行为与命运。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">想要逆袭，最大的难点，不是自己不够努力，而是有时我们付出的努力，不见成效。因为努力背后，总有一些不可逾越的鸿沟。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">那有没有捷径可以走？</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">有，改变你的思维模式。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">我国为什么实行教育兴国？保险公司为什么花重金投资在业务员的学习上？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">无疑就是要开拓认知，提升眼界，改变思维。学习优秀的思维，才能做出正确的行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; font-size: 18px;\">改变传统保险业的固化思维</span></p></section></section><section><section></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 20px;\">1<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">不要认为自己永远都只能做小单，签大单难。了解富人的思想，才能签下富人的单。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">总有人跟我说：“我做我的小单挺好的，上哪找大客户签大单去啊！我就先做做我的小单，等有机会了，我再去签大单。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">世界那么小，说不定哪一天机缘巧合你就认识到了马云或者王健林，你用跟普通人销售保险的那一套跟他说：“现在重大疾病的得病概率是70%，您得有一份重疾险。”我想他们一定不以为然，因为他们要的根本不是这种保障。你得了解富人到底需要什么，才能对症下药。</span></p></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;\">2<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">不要认为等到自己准备好签大单了</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">，再去找资源。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">中国人都是做踏实事的，有就人认为，我一定要将所有的事情准备好了我再去做某事。比如说买房，很多人攒了一辈子的钱，却无法攒够房价的涨幅。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">有些人认为，即使我现在没有能力做成某事，但是只要我认为这件事值得去做，我就整合所有资源去达到，而不会等到我有资源了我再去做。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">比如说我想做大单，我就想尽一切办法，整合一切资源，我也要拿下一个大单。只要我拿下过一次，第二次、第三次、我拿下的速度会越来越快，耗费的精力会越来越少，我累积到的就是签大的经验，我得到的回报，也将越来越多。</span></p></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px;\">3<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><strong style