th; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 25px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">老师笑了笑问我：“你知道为什么这个客户会选择信托而不选择保险吗？”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 25px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 25px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">我摇了摇头。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 22.4px;\">老师说，你不知道很正常，因为你不是高净值人群。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高净值客户的需求</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">远比我们想象的复杂</span></strong></p></section><section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); letter-spacing: 1px;\">她继续说道：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\">客户为什么会选信托，而不选择保险？<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 28px;\">那是因为他不知道保险具体能帮他解决什么问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\">信托是将自己的财产交给别人来打理。你可以反问客户：“您一个经历过大风大浪的人，难道还管理不好自己的资产吗？否则为什么要每年花十几万请别人去打理呢？”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\">其实客户并不是觉得自己没有能力来管理自己财富，而是担心自己的继承人没有这个能力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">那信托真正能够解决财富传承的问题吗？</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\">至少在中国，信托的发展历程决定了它是不如保险的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">所以说，这位伙伴其实是没有搞清楚，中国高净值人群配置保险的来龙去脉。</span></p></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个故事说明了一个问题：<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">高净值人群的需求隐藏的很深，远比我们想象中的要复杂。</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section><section><section></section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">财富规划的方式</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">远比我们想象的多</span></strong></p></section><section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">除了需求复杂，往往容易被忽略的一点是，高净值人群财富规划的方式也非常多，银行、信托、基金、债券都在他们的选择范围内，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 22.4px;\">当然还有保险</span>。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">久而久之，客户知道的财富管理方式并不比我们少，根据需求对比各种方式已经成了家常便饭。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.4px;\">想象一下，假如你是一名高净值人士，面对这么多方式和选择，肯定也会再三斟酌，谨慎决定。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.4px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.4px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">那作为一名保险代理人，又该如何让客户从众多选择中坚定不移的选择保险呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; text-align: justify;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; 