ong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">赵雪老师说:用Excel</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">赵雪老师将所有客户用编号式管理的方式列在Excel里</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">，每一个家庭的主要联系人的姓名上都有一个超链接，链接到一个文件夹，每一个文件夹里都有客户的所有详细资料。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\"></span><