lor: rgb(63, 63, 63); line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">长大后我们只有一个梦想，就是当——<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">有钱人</strong>。</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">我们一直幻想着有钱后会过上什么样的生活，结果发现自己错了，有钱人的生活是你根本想象不到的。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">有钱人的生活我们可能想象不到，但有钱人的风险是我们可以预知的。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">资产的风险，有一定的共性，也因如此，法律给予的可能会发生事件的共性一个评判的标准，换句话说，法律并不是为某一个人的特殊情况或资产的多少所制定。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">当我们不知风险会在何时何地发生时，学好法律能帮我们有效预防很多风险。</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">以前我听过这样一个对话：</span></p><p><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">A：您觉得钱存在妈妈那，安全吗？</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">B：当然安全，妈妈是应该世界上我们最应该放心的人。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">A：那你有没有想过，万一，只是万一，妈妈出了意外，这个钱应该是给谁的？</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">B：当然是归还给我。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">A：按照法律你和爸爸、还有姥姥都是第一顺位继承人，妈妈的资产是要平分给你们几个人的。<br/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">B：那我爸爸，姥姥肯定都不会要，最后都还是得给我。</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">A：姥姥可能是不会要，但是虽然姥姥不要，但属于姥姥的那一份资产，是属于姥姥名下的，姥姥过世后，资产是会有舅舅和姨的一份的。你敢保证舅舅和姨不会帮姥姥争夺吗？</span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; text-align: justify; line-height: 2em; clear: both; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 13px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\">当时那会这个小姑娘的舅舅和姨，正在争夺姥姥的房产。</span></p></section></section><p><br/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); clear: both; font-family:; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; -ms-word-wrap: b