cing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">法国有一个富翁，名叫巴拉昂，他在成为富翁之前过着非常贫穷的生活。一次偶然的机会，他开始推销装饰肖像画，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">迅速发家致富，居于法国五十大富翁之首。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">然而上天弄人，他不幸患上了前列腺癌。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在临终之前，他留下遗书：<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我曾是一位穷人，我并不想把自己成为富人的秘诀带入天堂，我已经把我的秘诀放进了银行我个人的保险箱里，并留下100万法郎作为揭开我秘诀谜底的奖金。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.45; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">若谁能够猜出我成为富人的秘诀，他就有权利拿走我保险柜中的100万法郎。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">遗书被刊登在报纸上，有四万多人投寄了自己的答案。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">有一些人认为穷人最缺少的是<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">金钱；</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">也有一些人认为，穷人最缺少的是</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">机会；</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">另外还有一些人认为穷人缺少的是</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">技能。</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">所有的答案应有尽有，各不相同。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5em;\">在巴拉昂逝世周年纪念日时，他的律师和代理人打开了银行内的那个保险箱公开了他致富的秘诀。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">在所有的来信中，只有一位名叫蒂勒的九岁女孩，猜出了正确的答案，她的答案是：<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“穷人最缺少的是野心。”</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">在颁奖之时，很多人都好奇的问<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">蒂勒</span>，你为什么会想到是野心?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px;\">蒂勒单纯地说：“我有一个姐姐，她每次把她的男朋友带回家时，总是警告我不要对她的男朋友产生野心，所以我在想，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">拥有野心应该可以使人得到自己想要的东西。</strong>”</span></p></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">这个故事听完让我恍然大悟。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">其实很多看似我们不可能完成的事，可能只是因为我们没有想要去完成它的野心，毕竟成功的例子不是没有。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">如果我们连想签千万保单的野心都没有，我们如何去迈出这一步并且想办法签下它呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><em class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 42px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2</em></section></section></section><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">你想签一张千万保单吗？</strong><section><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 28.8px;\"></span></strong></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">我们除了要有想签下千万保单的野心，我们还需要的是什么？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">学习！学习是成功最便捷的道路。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">大客户之间是存在共性的，他们一样都不缺钱，他们一样都认为自己不缺保障