(165, 165, 165); font-size: 14px;\">那做保险吧！不需要成本，不需要高难度技术，只要努力，只要坚持，这个行业将给予你千万种无法想象的回报。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\">保险这个行业的确有人月入百万，有人名车豪宅，但也有人节衣缩食仅为给客户送上一份促单礼……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">保险不管作为销售业还是服务业，永远的真理只有一条：<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">得客户者得天下</strong>。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">“送礼”作为中国文化的传统，许多人选择送礼给客户来助力我们成单、加保、转介绍，但不是每个人都有那么多本钱去给客户送礼，这对于刚入行的小年轻们体现的尤为明显。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 14px;\">很多刚入行的小年轻们，觉得自己没有一技之长，不会什么销售技巧，也用不好什么沟通技巧，不善于跟人打交道，好不容易学到一招，给客户送礼，却为钱的事情发愁。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-to